fields.content:
We’re interested in learning where your program is currently Active or Potential for access by students and educators. There are many programs that can serve wider audiences, particularly virtual ones. We want to help cross-pollinate organizations that do not have enough outreach or marketing. This effort is meant to support the growth and increased interaction of your programs.

Active - Program is currently operating in this state.

Potential - Your program is currently not active here, but it has the potential to expand to this state.

meta.description: If Approved, the Service Provider's Program record is updated and the workflow is then completed.
Once the form has been submitted, the Partner Organization must review and either Approve or Reject the submission.
meta.instructionsValue: Instructions: Please review the values in the fields below and click on the Approve or Needs Revision button. If updates are needed then the Provider will receive a notification to update their entry. You will need to review once more prior to approving and finalizing their updates. If there are minor changes to be made, simply approve their update and then edit their record directly.
